  "title": "Commercial Executive (Support)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ol>\n  <li>Responsible for handling RFQs within the time allocated, including receiving, creating, and distributing the quote to the client</li>\n  <li>Download customer inquiries and orders from various internet-based customer portals &amp; e-platforms (i.e. Ship-Serv, SisCommerce, BaseNet, MarineLink, B2B, etc)</li>\n  <li>Accurately update relevant information and line items in the company ERP system (D365 &amp; SCINT)</li>\n  <li>Perform any other duties as requested by the Commercial Director and/or line manager</li>\n</ol>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good spoken and written English</li>\n  <li>Excellent MS Office skills (Excel)</li>\n  <li>Able to work under constant deadline pressure</li>\n  <li>Team player with good interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Fast and accurate typing skills</li>\n</ul>",
